Statistics-Sequences version 0.01
=================================

Tests of sequential structure in the form of runs, joins, bunches, etc.
Includes the Wald-Walfowitz Runs test, and
Helmut Schmidt's test of the "potential energy", or pot, of runs.
Test of significance are limited to approximations from the normal distribution.
Provides methods for dichotomising data.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Class::OOorNO  
  Statistics::Descriptive
  Statistics::Zed
  Statistics::Distributions
  Statistics::Lite

